cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with the problem of recognition of handwritten character patterns, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of a feature set for effective recognition is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves experimentation with a database of samples, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
